Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.96,0:22:44.97,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H2324A6&}属于我们的前路在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:52.27,ED CN,,0,800,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H954115&}自己的梦想本该触手可及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:59.44,ED CN,,800,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H065253&}不料竟如此虚无缥缈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:06.28,ED CN,,800,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H053F8F&\t(3420,3421,\3c&H005C6A&)}慌乱不安之间时间飞逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.28,0:23:13.70,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H89830E&}厌倦身上重担的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:16.54,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&H89830E&}也变成了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.54,0:23:20.09,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&HA13655&}天空的祖母绿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:25.13,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&HA13655&}你究竟要传达怎样的启示？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:31.01,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&HA13655&}黎明到来 天边渐生微光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:39.69,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&HA13655&}碧绿的光芒冲破云霞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:49.66,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)\fscx110\3c&HA13655&}眼下似乎尚难称其为希望
